name: Corn Mission (Beta)
description:
Corn Mission is a 2d platform puzzle game with 2 different zones and 100 levels with more than 15 objects all with different mechanics. In addition, with 4 types of special levels each with unique gameplay.

The city of Avícola has run out of corn, your mission will be to search for corn in different areas and fill your sack with food, if you succeed you will save the city and Mother Hen will feel proud.

  • State: Developing
  • Genre: Puzzle
  • Number of levels: 100
  • Language: Spanish , English
  • Digital platforms: PC and Mobile phones 
  • Players: 1
  • Engine:Godot Engine 3.0
